# j e l l i c u l e Project Plan

## Overview
This document serves as the single source of truth for the j e l l i c u l e project, outlining the components, structure, and design principles.

## Directory Structure
```
/
├── dist/                  # Built library files
├── files/                 # Source files
│   └── components/        # Web component definitions
│       ├── forms/         # Form-related components
│       ├── interface/     # UI components
│       ├── layout/        # Layout components
│       └── text/          # Text-related components
├── pwa-service/           # Progressive Web App
│   ├── assets/            # Static assets
│   │   ├── icons/         # Icon files
│   │   ├── js/            # JavaScript files
│   │   └── styles/        # CSS files
│   └── index.html         # Main entry point
└── service/               # Server configuration
```

## Components Inventory

### Layout Components
- ActivityViewport: Main container for the application
- ActivityBar: Navigation bar that can be positioned on any side
- Activity: Individual navigation item within ActivityBar
- ActivityResizeButton: Button to resize ActivityBar
- Content: Container for main content
- MainContent: Primary content area
- Header: Page header
- Footer: Page footer
- Sidebar: Side navigation or content
- Viewport: Viewport container

### Interface Components
- Button: Interactive button element
- Icon: Iconography component
- List: List container
- Outline: Outline/border component
- Tag: Tag/label component

