## Design System

### Theme
- Retro-80s inspired design
- Two-tone color scheme: faded yellow and dark purple
- Wireframe aesthetic with chrome gradients
- Light (LCD) and dark (OLED) theme options

### Color Palette
- Primary: #f5d76e (Faded Yellow)
- Secondary: #4a235a (Dark Purple)
- Background Light: #f8f9fa (Light Gray)
- Background Dark: #121212 (Almost Black)
- Accent: linear-gradient(135deg, #c0c0c0, #f0f0f0, #c0c0c0) (Chrome Gradient)
- Text Light: #212529 (Dark Gray)
- Text Dark: #f8f9fa (Light Gray)
- Grid: #20c20e (Terminal Green)

### Typography
- Headings: "VT323", monospace (Retro terminal font)
- Body: "Press Start 2P", cursive (Pixel font)
- Fallback: monospace

