## Component Implementation Guidelines
1. Each component should have a fallback style for both light and dark themes
2. Components should accept custom styles via CSS variables
3. Components should be accessible and keyboard navigable
4. Components should work without JavaScript when possible
5. Components should be responsive and mobile-friendly

## Testing Strategy
1. Visual testing in multiple browsers
2. Accessibility testing
3. Responsive design testing
4. Performance testing

## Deployment Strategy
1. Build components into a single library file
2. Deploy PWA for demonstration
3. Publish documentation
